My fellow Michiganders, Run, don't walk.  This place nailed it on the head.  It was a simple formula that no other Coney in this state was able to do.  Take everything that people want from a Michigan Coney Island and mirror it here in the desert.  The coney dog and baby greek were spot on.  If I closed my eyes, I would think I was back in Michigan.  Kudos Detroit Coney.  This place makes me homesick.

